description:
My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 8

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

The competition is back in Queensland as couple David and Corinne are put to the test. Despite their 22 year age gap, love is all around for these two, but when cooking together against the clock, will their seafood themed night sink or swim?
